OL,7,FEthan Ives died in August 2021 from a
OL,8,Fcatastrophic brain injury. The
OL,9,Fprosecution claim the toddler was
OL,10,Fseriously assaulted from being shaken
OL,11,For receiving a blow to his head.
OL,13,FMichael Ives, 47, and Kerry Ives, 46,
OL,14,Fboth deny his murder and they, along
OL,15,Fwith their daughter Shannon Ives, 28,
OL,16,Ffrom near Holywell deny causing or
OL,17,Fallowing his death and child cruelty.
