OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FShe said it was her father Michael who
OL,8,Fwould mainly hit her. Miss Ives
OL,9,Frecalled living with her parents in
OL,10,FConnah's Quay when a box of locusts
OL,11,Fwere thrown over her by her father. He
OL,12,Fhad two bearded dragons as pets and
OL,13,Fthe locusts were food for them.
OL,15,FMiss Ives said he would also "kick me
OL,16,Fand say he didn't want me there."
OL,18,FShe told the court she left home at 16
OL,19,Fafter telling a councillor in college
OL,20,Fher father was being abusive.
