OL,7,FShe said she later moved back home
OL,8,Fafter splitting up from a partner she
OL,9,Fhad been living with and would sleep
OL,10,Fon a mattress in the dining room.
OL,12,FJurors at Mold Crown Court heard that
OL,13,Fshe split up with Ethan's dad before
OL,14,Fshe gave birth to their son but they
OL,15,Freunited during the pandemic and they
OL,16,Flived together.
OL,18,FDuring this time she said her parents
OL,19,Fwould visit her in Mold and her mother
OL,20,FKerry had said she had cancer, which
OL,21,Fturned out not to be true.
