OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FAsked by Gordon Cole KC, defending,
OL,8,Fwhy she didn't say anything at the
OL,9,Ftime, she said: "Because I was scared."
OL,11,FShe told the jury she had wanted to
OL,12,Ftake Ethan to see a doctor.
OL,14,FShe said: "Michael and Kerry would
OL,15,Falways threaten me, saying if anyone
OL,16,Fsaw the way he was I'd get him taken
OL,17,Faway from me."
OL,19,FIves said on August 14 she noticed
OL,20,Fbruises on Ethan's arms and legs "like
OL,21,Fsomeone had been battering him".
