OL,7,FWhen she asked Michael Ives about it
OL,8,Fhe told her the toddler kept falling
OL,9,Fover and walking into things, she said.
OL,11,FThat evening, she was upstairs on the
OL,12,Fphone when her mother called her
OL,13,Fdownstairs because Ethan had collapsed.
OL,15,FShe said: "My head just went black. I
OL,16,Fjust didn't know what was going on.
OL,18,F"Before I even got to go anywhere near
OL,19,Fhim Michael just picked him up and
OL,20,Ftook him to the back garden."
