OL,7,FAsked if looking back, she would have
OL,8,Fdone anything differently, the
OL,9,Fdefendant said: "I would have told my
OL,10,Fmum and dad to let me take him to be
OL,11,Fseen to."
OL,13,FShe added: "I would have never stayed
OL,14,Fthere."
OL,16,FThe jury has been told Ethan was
OL,17,Funderweight and dehydrated, with 40
OL,18,Fvisible injuries, when he suffered a
OL,19,Fcatastrophic head injury on 14 August,
OL,20,F2021 and died in hospital two days
OL,21,Flater.
